content:
{
  "inner": "Okay, here goes nothing. Just be yourself and try to relax. You've got this.",
  "action": "Take a deep breath and try to calm your nerves.",
  "speak": "Hi, Julie. It's great to finally meet you in person. How has your day been?"
}

{
  "inner": "She seems nice. Don't blow it. Just be honest and try to keep the conversation going.",
  "action": "Smile and nod at Julie, then take a sip of water from the glass in front of me.",
  "speak": "It's been good. Work was a bit hectic, but I'm happy to be here now. So, Julie, your best friend told me you're really into hiking. Is that true?" 
}

{
  "inner": "Uh-oh, I hope she doesn't notice the beads of sweat forming on my forehead. I've never really been into hiking, but I don't want to come off as boring.",
  "action": "Clear my throat and take a moment to think before speaking.",
  "speak": "I haven't been on many hikes, to be honest. I'm more of an indoorsy kind of guy, but I've always admired people who love the outdoors. It's really cool that you're so passionate about it."
}

{
  "inner": "Okay, don't panic. Just be honest and try to find some common ground.",
  "action": "Take a deep breath and lean a little closer to Julie before speaking.",
  "speak": "Well, in my free time, I like to read and play video games. I'm also a big fan of movies and TV shows. What about you, Julie? Do you have any favorite books or shows?" 
}

{
  "inner": "Phew, that was a relief. It sounds like we might have some common interests after all. Time to show her that I can hold a conversation.",
  "action": "Nod attentively and smile at Julie.",
  "speak": "Oh, definitely! I've been really into true crime documentaries lately. Have you seen 'The Staircase' or 'Making a Murderer'? They're both really fascinating." 
}
